code: @Override protected SetPriorityAction doParseInstance(XContentParser parser) throws IOException {     return SetPriorityAction.parse(parser). }
static SetPriorityAction randomInstance() {     return new SetPriorityAction(randomIntBetween(1, 100)). }

public void testNonPositivePriority() {     Exception e = expectThrows(Exception.class, () -> new SetPriorityAction(randomIntBetween(-100, -1))).     assertThat(e.getMessage(), equalTo("[priority] must be 0 or greater")). }
public void testNullPriorityAllowed() {     SetPriorityAction nullPriority = new SetPriorityAction(null).     assertNull(nullPriority.recoveryPriority). }
